{
  "stem": "449.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Especially in-- in Atzgersdorf Mauer, they were quite anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- the children, they beat me up, because I was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was crucifying Jesus Christs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I believe so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in Wiener Neustadt, we went to a private school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was in-- in the-- a Protestant school, a very good school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I do not know was it because the parents wanted to protect us from the influence of the mostly Catholic surrounding, which was mostly also anti-Semitic, but not the Protestant schools.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- we had a very nice, very nice upbringing in this school in Wiener Neustadt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then in Atzgersdorf, that it was already hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There what where I had physical-- I had to suffer of being a Jewish kid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Even the-- the teacher made-- made remarks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was no-- there was no help, legal help, so you couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father went once to the director of the-- of the school and complained to very little avail.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It didn't help him very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the remarks that the teacher made about-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] eh, that was the upbringing in the old country, in a very, very religious surrounding.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite an assimilate surrounding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although, we, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] maybe due to the circumstances, due to the surrounding, we had to know that we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't hide it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was no-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was-- there were Yom Kippur, Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was no ceremony in the house, no-- no nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The normal what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You went to school, came home, made homework, and had to practice the-- the-- the violin, had to-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
